{"type": "article", "id": 15865, "title": "NVy秋冬包饰", "description": "", "date": "2015-10-10T07:51:52Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 66, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000340lxdjmT6PUOI7fgko.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tNick Wooster 和日本时尚品牌 UNITED ARROWS &amp; SONS 的设计总监 Poggy 联合创办了一个新的品牌 NVy 。以”海军蓝“为主色调，结合了街头时尚与日式设计。自 9 月推出首个服饰系列之后又于近日推出了 8 件包饰单品。延续了深蓝色调和由  Komatsu Seiren Co. 加工的涤纶尼龙面料，十分耐用，整体呈现出硬朗的军事风格，适合秋冬季节和户外的场所。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143343GbH1sCXgtVO0fTrj.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143343NbUwiA08Rf61pBEg.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143344huNeLj2my6aA4bCT.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"682\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66601562\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143344ZwCUVDj87QRLWzs4.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143344oMiV21dT6gZ78wKx.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"682\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66601562\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143345YViuzhvy0ZfPO7s8.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"682\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66601562\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016072614334612NjHX6zFbngSB4K.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"682\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66601562\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"